reviewText: It didn't really have a lot of interesting stuff in it just a little bit about the Indians it's a little too slow and boring to me it's like sitting down to an extra long church service I can go to church and get this stuff

I never buy a product that I don't like...so in closing I love
everything that I bought...Thank you Amazon...Everything was awesome.
Powerful and so encouraging for those of us with Native American ancestry.
